articles.title: “No grid, no rules”: How the Spotify design team created the identity for this year's Wrapped - It's Nice That
articles.description: The campaign was partly inspired by chaos. And yet the visual identity has to be robust enough to work across countless countries, languages and formats. We hear how the team at Spotify grappled with this tricky challenge.
